1318
01:52:24,583 --> 01:52:26,542
Welcome home, Your Majesty.

1319
01:52:30,458 --> 01:52:32,000
I brought you something.

1320
01:52:32,083 --> 01:52:34,083
[both laughing]

1321
01:52:38,542 --> 01:52:39,542
My Queen.

1322
01:52:40,417 --> 01:52:42,417
- [both laughing]
- [Elizabeth yelps]

