1324
01:53:05,458 --> 01:53:11,792
<i>♪ I'm wearin' awa', John ♪</i>

1325
01:53:12,333 --> 01:53:18,542
<i>♪ Like snaw-wreaths in thaw, John ♪</i>

1326
01:53:19,042 --> 01:53:23,833
<i>♪ I'm wearin' awa' ♪</i>

1327
01:53:24,333 --> 01:53:31,083
<i>♪ To the land o' the leal ♪</i>

1328
01:53:32,708 --> 01:53:38,958
<i>♪ There's nae sorrow there, John ♪</i>

1329
01:53:39,417 --> 01:53:45,583
<i>♪ There's neither cauld nor care, John ♪</i>

1330
01:53:46,292 --> 01:53:51,167
<i>♪ The day is aye fair ♪</i>

1331
01:53:51,458 --> 01:53:57,833
<i>♪ In the land o' the leal ♪</i>

