1375
01:58:39,875 --> 01:58:45,583
<i>♪ We will drain our dearest veins ♪</i>

1376
01:58:45,792 --> 01:58:49,792
<i>♪ But they shall be free! ♪</i>

1377
01:58:51,250 --> 01:58:56,750
<i>♪ Lay the proud usurpers low! ♪</i>

1378
01:58:57,042 --> 01:59:02,542
<i>♪ Tyrants fall in every foe! ♪</i>

1379
01:59:02,667 --> 01:59:08,125
<i>♪ Liberty's in every blow! ♪</i>

1380
01:59:08,333 --> 01:59:12,625
<i>♪ Let us do or die! ♪</i>

1381
01:59:14,000 --> 01:59:19,042
<i>♪ Scots, wha hae wi' Wallace bled ♪</i>

1382
01:59:19,750 --> 01:59:25,250
<i>♪ Scots, wham Bruce has aften led ♪</i>

1383
01:59:25,542 --> 01:59:31,167
<i>♪ Welcome tae your gory bed ♪</i>

1384
01:59:31,375 --> 01:59:35,458
<i>♪ Or to victory ♪</i>

1385
01:59:45,667 --> 01:59:48,250
[cheering and applause]

